text: "2002" is a 2018 song by English singer Anne-Marie and written by Ed Sheeran. It went to the top ten in Australia, Austria, Czech Republic, Ireland, Malaysia, Scotland, Singapore, South Korea and the United Kingdom. It also made number 12 in New Zealand. == References == Category:2018 songs Category:2010s ballads Category:Anne-Marie (singer) songs
